00:28:11,973 --> 00:28:16,171
Hector. Very heroic name.
What makes you think it's a he?

358
00:28:16,344 --> 00:28:18,812
The size of the skull.
We found a female skull last week.

359
00:28:18,980 --> 00:28:20,675
