<i>Call me back.</i>

377
00:29:30,018 --> 00:29:31,576
BRIAN:
<i>Tib.</i>

378
00:29:32,620 --> 00:29:34,451
<i>It's Brian.</i>

379
00:30:00,215 --> 00:30:01,876
Oh!

380
00:30:02,050 --> 00:30:03,711
Okay.

381
00:30:11,526 --> 00:30:15,257
BRIDGET: <i>Lenny, I enclosed with the pants</i>
<i>a little bit of ancient dirt...</i>

382
00:30:15,430 --> 00:30:18,399
<i>... and a picture of me</i>
<i>with my new boyfriend, Hector.</i>

383
00:30:18,833 --> 00:30:22,963
<i>Not exactly the lively type,</i>
<i>but he's got the wisdom of the ages.</i>

384
00:30:52,066 --> 00:30:54,159
