Aren't you a little early?

385
00:30:54,736 --> 00:30:55,896
Oh.

386
00:30:56,070 --> 00:30:58,595
Pretty sure class doesn't start
for like 12 hours or so.

387
00:30:58,773 --> 00:31:03,073
