Cleo raised hers.

449
00:35:08,956 --> 00:35:12,392
Cleo had children? You can tell that?

450
00:35:12,560 --> 00:35:15,222
You can tell a lot from a skeleton.

451
00:35:15,396 --> 00:35:17,296
Look. Here.

452
00:35:18,766 --> 00:35:21,701
